<div class="leftColumn">

<h1>Welcome to Discover the World</h1>
<p>Ensuring a constant flow of new business is  essential to every organisation. Discover the World is the travel industry  expert at developing proven and innovative solutions to penetrate international  markets, drive market share and increase revenue.</p>
<p>We are passionate  about sales and marketing, helping our travel clients expand into new markets,  explore new sales channels, win new customers and realize their global  potential.</p>
<div class="more"> <a href="who-we-are.html" >Find out more</a> </div>
<div class="hr_home"></div>

<p><img src="images/bricks_clicks.gif" width="349" height="226" align="right" />As your partner we work to help you develop sales representation programs that meet your unique needs. Our recipe for success is simple. We listen to you. You tell us what you want to accomplish. Then we build.</p>
<p>It is about knowing you. It is about knowing who to target in each country to meet your objectives and deliver the desired result. It is about being your brand in the local market and delivering the right message to the right audience at the right time.</p>
<p>Today, we have more than 65 offices globally, bringing innovative sales and marketing solutions to a diverse client base to help solve their market expansion challenges. In addition to our core sales and marketing business, Discover the World is a technology leader, providing digital solutions through its innovative bigblueroad.com division.</p> 
<p>Our combined strength of talented local travel professionals and exciting online technology helps our clients increase profit, open new markets, retain and grow relationships, solve problems and service needs.</p>

<p>Others promise the world, we deliver it. <a href="contact-us.html" >Contact us</a> today.</p>
<div class="more"> <a href="what-we-do.html" >Find out more</a> </div>

